#Text=Kyle Kaplan
#Text=Kyle Joseph Kaplan ( born 16 July 1989 or 16 July 1990 ) is an American actor .
#Text=Life and career
#Text=At the age of 13 , Kaplan toured with Jim Henson 's Bear and the Big Blue House Live ! across the U.S. and United Kingdom for ten months .
#Text=He also performed at the Los Angeles Stage Ovation Awards in 2004 .
#Text=He is a member of a comedy improvisation troupe in Los Angeles .
#Text=Early in his career , he was the subject of a German filmmaker 's documentary called " Hollywood Kids " .
#Text=Kaplan 's current focus is on television and film .

#Text=He played Greg Grunberg 's nephew in NBC 's Grand Union sitcom pilot in 2005 and has appeared in several national commercials , including Wendy 's restaurants , Yahoo ! , Cingular Wireless , Simon Malls , Dairy Queen , and most recently , Honda .
#Text=He can be seen in a recurring role as Chad the Chomper in Disney 's Hannah Montana .
#Text=In 2006 , he also appeared in The Bernie Mac Show , CSI : Miami , and Zoey 101 .
#Text=In April 2006 , he completed filming on Chris Elliott 's semi-autobiographical sitcom pilot for CBS called " You 've Reached the Elliotts " playing the star 's son .

#Text=He filmed his 3rd pilot ( in less than a year ) in September , 2006 , as the son of actor/comedian/writer Tim Stack in the " Tim Stack 's Family Vacation " , a hybrid comedy ( part scripted , part improv ) produced for Nick at Nite .
#Text=Kaplan was then cast as Brian in The Oaks , a high concept family drama series for the Fox network set for production in 2008 , but was not picked up to series .
#Text=Kaplan was a recurring character on the Fox sitcom
#Text=The War at Home , and made guest appearances on the Fox sitcom The Winner , The Riches for the FX network .

#Text=He appeared in the Owen Wilson comedy Drillbit Taylor , and was cast in a leading role in Just Peck , a feature film which premiered at the Cannes Film Festival in 2009 , in which he plays the best friend of the title character , played by Keir Gilchrist .
#Text=Kaplan appears as Michael in the ABC Family sitcom 10 Things I Hate About You , based loosely on the 1999 film of the same name , which premiered July 7 , 2009 .
#Text=Music career
#Text=Since 2013 , Kaplan has been a part of the music duo Phantoms alongside Vinnie Pergola .
#Text=Their eponymous debut album was released in March 2017 .
